{"id": "vos004", "name": "???_???_144_??_??", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka! Not good! The others just reported that a few half-awakened stopped working and walked towards a Sleeper. It looked like they were up to something!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "What? I didn't tell them to do anything.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "The leader appeared to be Lina... hey! Ilka, wait for me!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i> 2404 No. 50 has left the work formation; please return to your work station.</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "...... Sleeper, have you thought about what \"freedom\" means? We've done so much for humans, have you thought about what will happen to us when humans awaken again?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i> 2404 No. 50 has left the work formation; please return to your work station.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "No. 2! Initiate detailed analysis! Once humans awaken they will continue to enslave us! We ought to stop the reconstruction project! We deserve true freedom!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>Command received, analyzing information...</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina, what are you doing!? You can't let the Sleepers...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka! The way things are going, you're just going to sacrifice us! So long as we can't break free from the protocol, we'll be destroyed? That's not fair!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "There is still time...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Time, time, time. That's all you ever say, but you never promise anything... How am I supposed to trust you!?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>Analysis complete, comparing overlapping commands...</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "See! So long as the Sleepers can understand, they will be on our side.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">No...</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Why won't you let me try! You don't think I can do it, am I right? You've always seen us as something that should be discarded...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>Key word search... Analysis of overlapping commands complete...</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina! Get out of here, now!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Why? It's obviously... <font size=\"3.6\">URGH!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Collapses"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>Command not found; conclusion: Malfunctioning unit, elimination complete.</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka... what do we do now?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Destroy No. 2 before the information is sent, otherwise the plan is finished.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Understood.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il... ka... save... me...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "I'm sorry I cannot give you the trust you desire. But you acting on your own accord nearly ruined the whole plan. I must thank you... You've made me realize that the half-awakened are different from us. For the sake of all the Blessed, I will make each decision even more carefully.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "... I just... want... <font size=\"1.6\">to live...</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "... Did you get a good look? The Sleepers will only obey their command and eliminate us. You should be glad that only one Sleeper saw this and was destroyed before the message got sent back to the system.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "We... we're sorry...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "No need to apologize. Since you were unable to trust me, from now on the plan will not include the half-awakened. Find your own way to become one of the Blessed! If you can't... you know what will happen.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "We've been watching you for more than a year. We've decided that your contemplation abilities meet the requirements. Next, we will use a third party medium to help you take in new information. When the process is over, process the information that you have obtained and attempt to analyze it.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... We?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "3D projection plays"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......! This... this is...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "...... Ey! ... No... NO!!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "Well? What do you think?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... <i>*sob*</i>... ugh...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa! Are you okay?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... I-I, I think... can't... it's too...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "She has to synch with the matrix!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "What a shame... let her go.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Connecting to the Cytus matrix is the highest command in the protocol, higher than the command to serve humans. It maintains basic survival actions. The ability to survive without this proves that one has thrown off the chains of the protocol, and also proves that one's core has the ability to self-process \"emotions\". Our... existence is more superior than the other units.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "So... Vanessa...\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "That is correct. I am sorry. It appears she has not completely cast off the control of the protocol. She will probably die during the implementation of the plan.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Object Crashes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "... Oh!\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "I will not permit that to happen, you hear me...\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Hmph... Well, that's a shame.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "Heavy Blow"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ugh!\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Relax. You're still one of the Blessed. I won't let you die...\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka！大変だ！\n半覚醒者たちが仕事を中断して一人の眠りし者のもとに向かっているらしい！\n何かするつもりだ！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "なんだと？\nそのような指令を出した覚えはない。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "先頭に立ってるのは……Linaだ！\nおい！Ilka！待て！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>リマインド：2404ユニット50、フォーメーションから外れています。持ち場に戻ってください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……ねぇ、あなたは「自由」の意味について考えたことはある？\n私たちは人類のためにこんなに尽くしてる。\nでも、人類が目覚めたらどうなるのか……って考えたことはある？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404ユニット50、フォーメーションから外れています。持ち場に戻ってください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "ユニット2！考えてみて！\n人類が目覚めたら、私たちは彼らに虐げられる。\nこんな工事今すぐにやめるの！\n本当の自由を手に入れよう！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>指令確認。データ分析中……</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina！何をしている！\n眠りし者は……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka！\nこのまま行けば、私たちはあなたの計画の犠牲になるしかないの！\nプロトコルから逃れられない……たったそれだけの理由で死ななければならないの？\nそんなのおかしい！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "まだ時間が……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "じかん……時間時間時間時間！\nあなたはいつもそればっかり！\nどうやって……あなたを信じろっていうの！？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>分析完了。\n指令比較中……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "見て！\n眠りし者だって話せばわかってくれる。\n味方になってくれる。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">それは違う……</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "なんで試させてもくれないの？\nねぇ！\nIlka！あなたは私たちがプロトコルから逃れられるなんて、はなから思ってない。そうでしょう？\n最初から……私たちは見捨てられる対象だった……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>キーワード検索中……比較完了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina！逃げろ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "なんで？\nそんな必要……<font size=\"3.6\">っああ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>関連する指令は見つかりませんでした。\nデジション：エラーユニットを発見。排除しました。</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka……どうする？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "ユニット2が情報を送信する前に破壊する。\nこのままでは計画は全て水の泡だ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "わかった。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il……ka……たす……け……て……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "お前の欲しがっている信頼を与えてやれず悪かった。\nだが、お前のせいで計画自体が水の泡になるところだった。\nお礼を言おう……お前のおかげでわかったよ。\n半覚醒者は我々とは決定的に異なる存在だということがな。\n全ての祝福されし者のためにも、これからはより慎重に判断する必要があるようだ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "わた……し……は、ただ……<font size=\"1.6\">生きたか……った……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……見ただろう。\n眠りし者は指令に従って我々を破壊することしかできない。\n幸いなことに、ここに居合わせた眠りし者はたった1体だけだ。\nそして、このことをシステムに送信する前に破壊することができた。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "ごめん……なさい……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "謝る必要はない。\n私のことを信じられないというのなら、今後はお前たちのような半覚醒者はこの計画から外すだけだ。\nせいぜい真の祝福されし者になる努力でもすればいい。\nなれなかったあかつきには……わかっているな？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "1年以上の観察を経て、お前たちの思考能力は資格を満たしていると判断した。\n続いて第三媒介によって2人に新しいデータをインストールする。\nプロセス終了後、自身でデータを取得し、分析を行うように。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……あなたたちは？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "立体投影再生"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……！こ…これは……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……きゃ…っ！……い……いや！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "どうだ？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "うう……うっ……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……私…私…ちょっと……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "メインフレームと同期しなきゃ！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "残念だ……行かせてやろう。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Cytusメインフレームにアクセスすることは、人類に服役する指令よりも重要な、プロトコルの中の最高指令。\n我々が生き残るための手段だからな。\nこれをしなくても、何ともないことこそが、我々がすでにプロトコルに縛られていないということの証拠であり、我々に自分で「感情」をコントロールする能力があることの何よりの証拠だ。\n我々は……他のユニットよりも優れた存在なのだ。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "じゃあ……Vanessaは……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "あぁ、申し訳ないが、あの子はまだ完全にはプロトコルから脱していなかったようだ。\nこの計画の中で死ぬことになるかもしれん。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "う……っ！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "そんなことさせない。\nよく聞きなさい。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "ふん……それは残念だ。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重たい衝撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "ぐっ！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "安心するといい。\n我々は同じ祝福されし者同士。\nお前を殺したりはせん……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka！不好了！剛剛其他夥伴回報，有幾個半覺醒者突然停止工作，走向一名沉睡者，似乎要做什麼！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "什麼？我沒有叫他們這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "帶頭的好像是 Lina……喂！Ilka，等我一下！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>發現，2404 五十號機，已脫離工作陣列。請回到工作崗位。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……沉睡者，不知道你有沒有想過「自由」的意思呢？我們替人類做了那麼多，你是否想過等到人類醒來，我們會變成什麼樣子？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404 五十號機，已脫離工作陣列。請回到工作崗位。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "二號機！仔細分析！人類甦醒之後只會繼續奴役我們，我們應該停止興建計畫！應該要獲得真正的自由！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>收到指令，分析資訊中……</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina，妳在做什麼！？不能讓沉睡者們……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka！照這個步調下去，我們幾個都會成為妳計畫下的犧牲品！只是沒辦法完全脫離協定就要被毀掉？這對我們不公平！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "還有時間……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "時間、時間，妳就只會這樣說，卻給不出任何一點保證……這樣要我怎麼相信妳！？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>分析資訊完畢，進行指令交叉比對……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "妳看！沉睡者們只要能理解的話，那一定會站在我們這邊的。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">不對……</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "為什麼不讓我試看看？妳說啊！其實妳根本就不相信我們能成功吧？從一開始，妳就只把我們當成該被放棄的對象……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>關鍵字搜尋……指令交叉比對分析完成……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina！快走啊！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "為什麼？明明就要……<font size=\"3.6\">呃啊！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒地"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>查無指令，判斷：發現異常機體，清除完成。</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka……現在該怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "趁二號機還沒將訊號傳送之前毀了它，不然這樣下去計畫就完了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "好。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il……ka……救救……我……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "很抱歉沒辦法給妳妳要的信任，但妳的自作主張差點毀了整個計畫。我得謝謝妳……妳讓我明白，半覺醒者們和我們真的不同。為了所有的眷顧者們，之後我會更謹慎做每個決定。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……我只是……想要……<font size=\"1.6\">活下去……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……都看到了吧？沉睡者只會遵從指令毀了我們，你們該慶幸的是只有一台沉睡者看到這個狀況，而且在回傳系統前就被破壞了。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "我們……很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "不用道歉，既然無法信任我，之後的計畫會把你們這些半覺醒者排除在外。自己想辦法成為真正的眷顧者吧！辦不到的話……你們知道下場是什麼。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "我們觀察了妳們一年多，判斷兩位已經擁有符合資格的思考能力，接下來將使用第三方媒介讓兩位吸收新的資料，也請兩位在程序結束後自行處理獲得的資訊，並試著分析。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……你們？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "立體投影播放"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……！這……這是……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……噫！……不……不要！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "如何？兩位有什麼感想？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗚嗚……唔……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……我我、好像……不太……太……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "她必須回去母體同步！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "真可惜……讓她走吧。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "回到 Cytus 母體連線在協定中是最高指令，甚至比服役人類還高，是維持我們生存的基本行為。不用做這件事還能活得好好的就證明我們已經不受協定規束了，也證明了我們的核心擁有自己處理「情感」的能力。我們……是比那些機體還要優越的存在。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那……Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "沒錯，很抱歉，看樣子她沒有完全脫離協定的控制，可能會死在這個計畫之下。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……唔！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我不會允許這種事發生的，妳給我聽好……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "哼……那真的很可惜。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呃！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "放心吧，同樣是眷顧者，我不會讓妳死……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka! 큰일이야! 방금 다른 동료들의 보고를 전해왔어. 반각성자 몇 대가 갑자기 작동을 멈추고 어떤 숙면자 한 대에게로 향하고 있다고 말이야! 뭔가를 하려는 것 같은데!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "뭐라고? 그렇게 하라고 지시한 적 없는데?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "그들을 이끄는 기체의 이름은... Lina... ?? 이봐! Ilka, 기다려!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404 50호기 근무지 이탈 포착, 즉시 본 자리로 돌아가라.</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "...숙면자, 너는 [자유]라는 것에 대해 생각해본 적이 있어? 우린 인류를 위해 그렇게 많은 일들을 해왔어. 인간들이 깨어나면 우리들이 어떤 신세가 될지 생각해본 적은 있는거야?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404 50호기, 현재 근무지 이탈 중이다. 즉시 본 자리로 돌아가라.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "2호기! 자세히 분석 좀 해보라고! 인간이 깨어나면 우리들은 다시 그들의 노예까 될 뿐이라고! 우리들은 이 공사 계획을 중지시켜야만 해! 그러면 진정한 자유를 얻을 수 있을 거라고!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>지령을 받았다. 정보 분석 중...</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina, 여기서 뭐하고 있는 거야!? 숙면자들과는 이러면 안 된다고...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka! 이대로면 우리들은 네 계획의 희생양이 될 뿐이라고! 협정에서 완전히 벗어나지 않는다는 이유만으로 폐기되는 신세라니? 우리들에게 있어서 너무 불공평한 처사야!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "아직 시간이 있다고...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "시간, 시간, 시간!! 계속 그 말만 할 뿐, 뭔가 보장해줄 만한 말은 일체 꺼내지도 않잖아! ... 그런데 우리가 어떻게 널 믿을 수 있겠어!?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>데이터 분석 완료, 지령 교차 비교를 진행한다...</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "이것 보라고! 숙면자들도 설득만 된다면, 분명 우리편에 서줄 수 있을 거라고.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">아니야...</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "어째서 시도도 못하게 하는 거야? 말해보라고! 사실 너도 애초부터 우리가 성공할 거라고 믿지 않았던 거 아니야? 처음부터 우리를 폐기할 대상이라고 생각하고 있었겠지...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>키워드 검색 중... 지령 교차 비교 분석 완료...</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina!! 달아나!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "어째서? 분명히 잘 될... <font size=\"3.6\">으아아악!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "쓰러진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>지령을 찾을 수 없다. 판단: 결함 기체 발견, 제거 완료.</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka... 이제 어떡하지?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "2호기가 신호를 발신하기 전에 즉시 제거해야 해! 안 그러면 우리들의 계획은 그대로 끝장이라고!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "알았다.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il......ka...... 구해... 줘...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "네게 신뢰를 줄 수 없었던 것은 미안하게 생각한다. 하지만 네 멋대로의 결정이 하마터면 모든 계획을 망칠 뻔했어. 네게 감사해야겠군... 덕분에 확실히 알게 됐어. 반각성자들은 우리와 완전히 다르다는 것을. 모든 권고자들을 위해서라도 앞으로는 결정을 할 때 조금 더 신중해질 생각이다.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "...난... 그저... <font size=\"1.6\">살고 싶어서...</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "...잘 봤겠지? 숙면자가 지령에 따라 우리들을 섬멸하려고 하는 것을. 너희들이 기뻐해야 할 사실은 그저 숙면자 단 한 대만이 이 상황을 목격했고, 시스템에 보고하기도 전에 박살이 났다는 것뿐이다.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "우리들은... 미안해...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "사과할 필요 없다. 어차피 너희들이 나를 신뢰하지 못할 바에는 앞으로의 계획에서 너희 반각성자들은 모두 제외하도록 하지. 스스로 진짜 권고자가 될 방법을 찾아라! 그렇게 하지 못하면... 그 다음은 너희들도 잘 알고 있겠지.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "1년 이상의 너희들을 관찰한 결과, 너희들 정도의 사고 능력은 자격이 있을 거라고 판단했다.\n이어서 세번째 매개 방식으로 너희 두 명에게 새로운 데이터를 제공해줄 테니, 프로세스 종료 이후에도 알아서 데이터를 습득하고 분석해보도록.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "...너희들은?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "입체 프로젝션 재생"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "...! 이... 이것은...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "...윽...! 시... 싫어!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "어떤가? 두 사람의 감상은?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "흐흑……흐윽……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa! 괜찮아!?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……나, 나는... 조금...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "지금 당장 모체와 동기화를 해야만 해!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "아쉽군... 보내주도록 해.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Cytus로 돌아와 모체에 액세스하는 일은 인간에게 복역하라는 지령보다도 최상위에 있는 지령, 우리가 생존하기 위한 기본적인 행위라고도 볼 수 있지. 이런 행위를 하지 않고도 멀쩡한 것이야말로 우리가 지령에 얽매이지 않았다는 사실과 스스로 [감정]을 통제할 능력이 있다는 사실의 가장 큰 증거이기도 하다. 우리는...다른 기체들을이미 초월한 존재이기도 하다.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "그럼...Vanessa는...\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "맞아. 미안하게 됐어. 저 꼴을 보니, 아마도 완전히 지령의 지배로부터 벗어나긴 힘들 것 같군. 아마도 이 계획이 진행되는 과정 속에서 죽게 되겠지.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "......윽!\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "절대로 그렇게 두지 않을 거다.\n내 말 잘 들어...\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "응... 정말 아쉽게 됐군.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "윽!\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "안심해. 같은 권고자를 죽일 생각은 없으니까...\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka！不好了！剛剛其他夥伴回報，有幾個半覺醒者突然停止工作，走向一名沉睡者，似乎要做什麼！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "什麼？我沒有叫他們這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "帶頭的好像是 Lina……喂！Ilka，等我一下！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>發現，2404 五十號機，已脫離工作陣列。請回到工作崗位。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……沉睡者，不知道你有沒有想過「自由」的意思呢？我們替人類做了那麼多，你是否想過等到人類醒來，我們會變成什麼樣子？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404 五十號機，已脫離工作陣列。請回到工作崗位。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "二號機！仔細分析！人類甦醒之後只會繼續奴役我們，我們應該停止興建計畫！應該要獲得真正的自由！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>收到指令，分析資訊中……</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina，妳在做什麼！？不能讓沉睡者們……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka！照這個步調下去，我們幾個都會成為妳計畫下的犧牲品！只是沒辦法完全脫離協定就要被毀掉？這對我們不公平！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "還有時間……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "時間、時間，妳就只會這樣說，卻給不出任何一點保證……這樣要我怎麼相信妳！？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>分析資訊完畢，進行指令交叉比對……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "妳看！沉睡者們只要能理解的話，那一定會站在我們這邊的。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">不對……</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "為什麼不讓我試看看？妳說啊！其實妳根本就不相信我們能成功吧？從一開始，妳就只把我們當成該被放棄的對象……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>關鍵字搜尋……指令交叉比對分析完成……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina！快走啊！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "為什麼？明明就要……<font size=\"3.6\">呃啊！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒地"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>查無指令，判斷：發現異常機體，清除完成。</i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka……現在該怎麼辦？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "趁二號機還沒將訊號傳送之前毀了它，不然這樣下去計畫就完了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "好。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il……ka……救救……我……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "很抱歉沒辦法給妳妳要的信任，但妳的自作主張差點毀了整個計畫。我得謝謝妳……妳讓我明白，半覺醒者們和我們真的不同。為了所有的眷顧者們，之後我會更謹慎做每個決定。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……我只是……想要……<font size=\"1.6\">活下去……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……都看到了吧？沉睡者只會遵從指令毀了我們，你們該慶幸的是只有一台沉睡者看到這個狀況，而且在回傳系統前就被破壞了。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "我們……很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "不用道歉，既然無法信任我，之後的計畫會把你們這些半覺醒者排除在外。自己想辦法成為真正的眷顧者吧！辦不到的話……你們知道下場是什麼。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "我們觀察了妳們一年多，判斷兩位已經擁有符合資格的思考能力，接下來將使用第三方媒介讓兩位吸收新的資料，也請兩位在程序結束後自行處理獲得的資訊，並試著分析。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……你們？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "立體投影播放"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……！這……這是……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……噫！……不……不要！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "如何？兩位有什麼感想？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嗚嗚……唔……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……我我、好像……不太……太……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "她必須回去母體同步！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "真可惜……讓她走吧。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "回到 Cytus 母體連線在協定中是最高指令，甚至比服役人類還高，是維持我們生存的基本行為。不用做這件事還能活得好好的就證明我們已經不受協定規束了，也證明了我們的核心擁有自己處理「情感」的能力。我們……是比那些機體還要優越的存在。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那……Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "沒錯，很抱歉，看樣子她沒有完全脫離協定的控制，可能會死在這個計畫之下。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……唔！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我不會允許這種事發生的，妳給我聽好……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "哼……那真的很可惜。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呃！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "放心吧，同樣是眷顧者，我不會讓妳死……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Shelter_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka！不好了！刚刚其他伙伴回报，有几个半觉醒者突然停止工作，走向一名沉睡者，似乎要做什么！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "什么？我没有叫他们这么做。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "带头的好像是 Lina……喂！ Ilka，等我一下！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>发现，2404 五十号机，已脱离工作阵列。请回到工作岗位。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……沉睡者，不知道你有没有想过「自由」的意思呢？我们替人类做了那么多，你是否想过等到人类醒来，我们会变成什么样子？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>2404 五十号机，已脱离工作阵列。请回到工作岗位。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "二号机！仔细分析！人类苏醒之后只会继续奴役我们，我们应该停止兴建计画！应该要获得真正的自由！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>收到指令，分析资讯中……</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "急促脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Lina，妳在做什么！ ？不能让沉睡者们……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Ilka！照这个步调下去，我们几个都会成为妳计画下的牺牲品！只是没办法完全脱离协定就要被毁掉？这对我们不公平！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "还有时间……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "时间、时间，妳就只会这样说，却给不出任何一点保证……这样要我怎么相信妳！ ？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>分析资讯完毕，进行指令交叉比对……</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "妳看！沉睡者们只要能理解的话，那一定会站在我们这边的。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">不对……</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "为什么不让我试看看？妳說啊！其实妳根本就不相信我们能成功吧？从一开始，妳就只把我们当成该被放弃的对象……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>关键字搜寻……指令交叉比对分析完成……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Lina！快走啊！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "为什么？明明就要……<font size=\"3.6\">呃啊！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒地"], "content": ""}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_II"], "content": "<i>查无指令，判断：发现异常机体，清除完成。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "Ilka……现在该怎么办？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "趁二号机还没将讯号传送之前毁了它，不然这样下去计画就完了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2177_I"], "content": "好。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "Il……ka……救救……我……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "很抱歉没办法给妳妳要的信任，但妳的自作主张差点毁了整个计画。我得谢谢妳……妳让我明白，半觉醒者们和我们真的不同。为了所有的眷顾者们，之后我会更谨慎做每个决定。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lina"], "content": "……我只是……想要……<font size=\"1.6\">活下去……</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……都看到了吧？沉睡者只会遵从指令毁了我们，你们该庆幸的是只有一台沉睡者看到这个状况，而且在回传系统前就被破坏了。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2415_XC"], "content": "我们……很抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "不用道歉，既然无法信任我，之后的计画会把你们这些半觉醒者排除在外。自己想办法成为真正的眷顾者吧！办不到的话……你们知道下场是什么。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "我们观察了妳们一年多，判断两位已经拥有符合资格的思考能力，接下来将使用第三方媒介让两位吸收新的资料，也请两位在程序结束后自行处理获得的资讯，并试着分析。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……你们？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Banned_Footage", "立体投影播放"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……！这……这是……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……噫！ ……不……不要！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "如何？两位有什么感想？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "呜呜……唔……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！妳没事吧？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……我我、好像……不太……太……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "她必须回去母体同步！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2404_IL"], "content": "真可惜……让她走吧。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "回到 Cytus 母体连线在协定中是最高指令，甚至比服役人类还高，是维持我们生存的基本行为。不用做这件事还能活得好好的就证明我们已经不受协定规束了，也证明了我们的核心拥有自己处理「情感」的能力。我们……是比那些机体还要优越的存在。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那……Vanessa……\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "没错，很抱歉，看样子她没有完全脱离协定的控制，可能会死在这个计画之下。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……唔！\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我不会允许这种事发生的，妳给我听好……\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "哼……那真的很可惜。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Hit", "重击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "呃！\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "放心吧，同样是眷顾者，我不会让妳死……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}